	system_input.c (system_input_update, emit_key, handle_event,
	set_mute, set_fullscreen, set_paused): make key bindings
	configurable, add joystick support.

	* system_comms.c: implement network play (not working)

	* system_graphics.c: add yuv overlay support, rewrite pixel format
	conversion and blocky scaling.

	* system_graphics.c (system_graphics_update), system_hq_intern.h,
	system_hq2x.c, system_hq2x.h, system_hq3x.c, system_hq3x.h: add
	HQ2x/HQ3x scaler (from scummvm).

	* system_io.c (validate_dir): create all non-existing components
	of directory, not only last.

	* system_io.c (system_state_load, system_state_save,
	system_io_flash_read, system_io_flash_write,
	system_make_file_name), system_screenshot.c (get_screenshot_name):
